- 统计结果：`{{ (artifacts.get("tables") or {}).get("differential_results", (artifacts.get("tables") or {}).get("top_features", "not_recorded")) }}`
- 图表目录：`{{ (artifacts.get("figures") or {}).get("pca", (artifacts.get("figures") or {}).get("heatmap", "not_recorded")) }}`
